Description: Network-wide outage longer than BreakThresholdSecs triggers ASERT re-anchor on the recovery block; on-chain difficulty must decay during the outage and the anchor must advance to the recovery block.
Network: ./zombienet.toml
Creds: /tmp/zn-creds.cfg

sleep 120 seconds

alice: pause
bob: pause
charlie: pause
dave: pause

eve: js-script ./wait-difficulty-halved.js return is 1 within 600 seconds

alice: resume

eve: js-script ./assert-anchor-reset.js return is 1 within 600 seconds
